{"tid":1840301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三個關員犧牲，就係為守護香港邊境","createTime":"2020-01-24T18:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T05:47:26.000Z","uid":77905,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1ce46f8c08b35f5ef2f68e8c493ce82f78bb03","tid":1840301,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:59:28.000Z","msg":"三個香港海關關員犧牲，就係為守護香港邊境<br />\n當時海關淺水巡邏船做緊反走私巡邏行動<br />\n被撞翻船，船上海關人員三死兩傷<br />\n<br />\n其中一個海關人員好年輕，27歲，入職兩至三年<br />\n另外一個39歲男署理沙展<br />\n而船隻指揮官係43歲女沙展，屋企有三個小朋友<br />\n<br />\n涉事海關巡邏艇當時發現兩艘走私凍肉既船，上前追截<br />\n走私客全部跳上同一艘船高速駛離<br />\n另一艘沒有亮燈的走私船則被棄下<br />\n海關巡邏艇追截時疑未察該棄船，直撞引致翻船<br />\n<br />\n走私凍肉可能係死豬 又或者病豬<br />\n流入市面可大可少<br />\n<br />\n其實都係想同大家講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港邊境係必須要大家一齊守護</span><br />\n今次香港係生係死 <br />\n大家一齊上"},{"pid":"d3708d42a0ee98a0658d3cb41ec2da9e6b04b5ec","tid":1840301,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1qB775V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1qB775V.jpg&h=a4cc2576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[封印高鐵] <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">高鐵不封 ! </span>港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵 !  香港封關 ! </span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1840241/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1840241/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e7b4a0786e6ee74f74a4077d39d6ced7f5b84c93","tid":1840301,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"ec1a1110c1737c5dcd1be15300d803556b7cdb8b","tid":1840301,"uid":205844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"香港海關respect...."},{"pid":"c3a040e9b99425167278fe031f56bd7e53ea47bb","tid":1840301,"uid":195540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:01:58.000Z","msg":"早排有批豬免費派？<br />\n利申鳩估 唔